The AH team determined that the member would need to use TR for the 1/9/23 term and could start to use TA for the 5/8/23 term (case 07265704). They submitted reimbursement request 325060 for the 1/9/23 term and it was approved on 4/14/23 for $5124.00. However, TA was also invoiced and sent to the EP for the same term in the amount of $5124.00. This has led to a double-payment for the 1/9/23 term and a TA reverse override is approved.
